as.description: The element or component this component should render as. Can be overwrite by asChild
as.description_zh: 此组件应呈现为的元素或组件。可以被 asChild 覆盖

asChild.description: Change the default rendered element for the one passed as a child, merging their props and behavior.
asChild.description_zh: 更改作为子元素传递的默认渲染元素，合并其道具和行为。

active.description: Used to identify the link as the currently active page.
active.description_zh: 用于将链接标识为当前活动页面。

:onSelect.description: Event handler called when the user selects a link (via mouse or keyboard). Calling event.preventDefault in this handler will prevent the navigation menu from closing when selecting that link.
:onSelect.description_zh: 当用户选择链接（通过鼠标或键盘）时调用的事件处理程序。在此处理程序中调用 event.preventDefault 将防止在选择该链接时关闭导航菜单。
